snippet.title: Amber Heard FIRED from Aquaman 2 Because She's TOO FAT to Play Mera?!
snippet.description:
Amber Heard is RUMORED to have been fired from Aquaman 2 for violating the "physical fitness" clause of her contract, and that she may be replaced with Emilia Clarke. So is Heard to fat to play Mera, or is it just a smokescreen for Warner Bros. to get rid of her after repeated PR disasters in the wake of the Depp case?
